    "body" : "<p>If you are using IntelliJ IDEA or Android Studio:</p>\n\n<p><img src=\"https://i.sstatic.net/0k4Pv.png\" alt=\"Android optimize imports\"></p>\n\n<p>Go to <strong>Settings <kbd>></kbd> Editor <kbd>></kbd> General <kbd>></kbd>Auto Import</strong> and check the <strong>Optimize imports on the fly</strong> checkbox.</p>\n"
