    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 3.0",
    "body" : "<p><strong>Choose the project/module</strong> you want to remove unused import from in Project view. Then from <strong>Code</strong> menu choose <strong>Optimize imports</strong> and confirm with <strong>Run</strong>. The imports will be cleaned in whole project/module.</p>\n"
