    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
    "body" : "<p>To remove the unused imports in windows. please use the default key combination below.</p>\n<p><strong><code>CTRL + ALT + O    ---&gt; to remove the unused imports in windows.</code></strong></p>\n<p>However, you can also change the keymap of <strong>&quot;Optimize Imports&quot; in settings.</strong></p>\n"
